{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"EventSource.close()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/close","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/EventSource\"><code>EventSource()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/url\"><code>url</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/withCredentials\"><code>withCredentials</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><em><code>close()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/open_event\"><code>open</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>close()</code></strong> method of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource\"><code>EventSource</code></a>\n  interface closes the connection, if one is made, and sets the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventSource/readyState\"><code>EventSource.readyState</code></a> attribute to <code>2</code> (closed).\n</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><